MASSIVE NAVAL BATTLE - Napoleon Total War - Darth Mod Gameplay - Today we are going to set sail in an epic battle. Today we are playing a naval battle in Napoleon Total War Darth Mod. Jackiefish will be joining me as the United Kingdoms, and I play as Portugal. We face a combined force of Ottomans and French. Enjoy the Naval Battle! :D

Sultan's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnbVfcV2QNdg2ApY12-AgZQ

Jackie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jackiefishhhhhh

Darth Mod: http://www.moddb.com/mods/darthmod-napoleon

JOIN MY DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.gg/JjR7UR3
